data.description: Home in a quiet neighborhood of Norristown. Enter into the nicely sized first floor featuring brand new flooring throughout, a living room, spacious dining room and kitchen with brand new appliances. The kitchen has access to the fenced-in backyard. Upstairs is fully carpeted, featuring 2 good sized bedrooms. Home is conveniently located to major highways, local shops, and dining.  Buyer will be responsible for U&O
